ires that felonies be tried only upon indictment by a grand jury. Federal grand juries can force people to take the witness stand, but defendants in those proceedings have Fifth Amendment privileges until they choose to answer any question. To claim the privilege for failure to answer when being interviewed by police, the interviewee must have explicitly invoked the constitutional right when declining to answer questions."]], "steps": [{"stage": "router", "label": "MULTI_HOP", "raw": "MULTI_HOP"}, {"stage": "round_1", "query": "What was the percentage the Dow Jones fell during the time the first cake mix come out?", "raw_output": "The question asks for the percentage the Dow Jones fell during the time the first cake mix came out. The relevant passage is passage 3, which states that the first cake mix was patented during the Great Depression to provide easily made food to millions of economically depressed people in the United States.

